**Privacy Policy**

**Last Updated: [24.02.2025]**

Welcome to **OG Lab**! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website **https://oglab.com/** and use our services.

### 1. **Information We Collect**
We collect only the minimal amount of personal data necessary to provide our services effectively. This may include:
- Name and contact details (if you voluntarily provide them for orders or inquiries).
- Payment information (processed securely by third-party payment providers, we do not store credit card details).
- Technical data (IP address, browser type, and cookies) for website optimization and security.

### 2. **How We Use Your Information**
We use collected data for:
- Processing orders and delivering cannabis products in accordance with Thai law.
- Improving our websiteâ€™s functionality and user experience.
- Communicating with you regarding your orders, inquiries, or special promotions (only if you opt-in).
- Ensuring compliance with legal and regulatory requirements in Thailand.
- Providing educational information about **our cannabis farm, dispensary, cannabis shop, and Andaman papirosa manufacturing**. Please note that we do not sell products online; all purchases must be made through our authorized offline partners.

### 3. **Cookies and Tracking Technologies**
We use cookies to enhance website functionality and analyze traffic. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.

### 4. **Sharing of Data**
We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties, except in the following cases:
- When required by Thai law or regulatory authorities.
- To process payments securely via trusted third-party services.
- In case of a business transaction (e.g., a merger or acquisition), where data transfer is necessary.

### 5. **Data Security**
We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.

### 6. **Your Rights**
You have the right to:
- Access, update, or delete your personal data.
- Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time.
- Request information about how we handle your data.

To exercise these rights, contact us at **[your contact email]**.

### 7. **Legal Compliance**
OG Lab operates in full compliance with Thai cannabis regulations. We do not sell products to individuals under the legal age or outside permitted jurisdictions. All information provided on our website is for **educational purposes only**, and any purchases must be made through our offline partners.

### 8. **Changes to This Policy**
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page, and significant updates may be communicated via email.

### 9. **Contact Us**
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at **[contact@oglab.com]**.

By using our website, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

